Skype Log Viewer LGG V 1.1
If you are having trouble, please make sure to check these common issues.
Q. No conversations are shown in the left drop down A. You need to direct the program to your main.db file that skype uses, it is normally found in your skype's application folder
Q. Still no conversations are show, or error appears A. You may need to close skype first before using this program
Q. I click a conversation but nothing happens. A. You need to double click to trigger a load command
Q. I double click a conversation but nothing happens. A. This process can take time, keep a eye on the progress bar on the bottom
Q. I am unable to save or export logs A. You may need to disable UAC or run this program as administrator.
Q. I need more specific help A. Please email lordgreggreg@gmail.com with a detailed explanation of the issue.
